 technique for identifying\nand tracking BPs have allowed us to determine reliable parameters of these\nfeatures in the internetwork. Thus we find, e.g., that they are considerably\nlonger lived than previously thought. The large velocities are also reliable,\nand may excite kink waves. Although these wave are (marginally) energetic\nenough to heat the quiet corona, we expect a large additional contribution from\nlarger magnetic elements populating the network and partly also the\ninternetwork.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 20 Nov 2012 19:24:59 GMT"}],"update_date":"2013-01-29"}
