, we conclude, would make much of the\nplanet uninhabitable by humans, thus calling into question strategies that\nemphasize adaptation to climate change.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 20 Nov 2012 19:47:15 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 2 Apr 2013 19:21:13 GMT"}],"update_date":"2014-03-05"}
