f\nsuperparamagnetism. The frequency dependence of the peak of ac susceptibility\nobeys the Vogel-Fulcher law with $\\tau_0\\approx 10^{-9}$ s. This together with\nthe existence of an AT line in H-T space indicates the existence of significant\ninter-cluster interaction among these ferromagnetic-clusters.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 21 Nov 2012 04:55:56 GMT"}],"update_date":"2012-11-22"}
